Text:
This app will install Beats Audio driver to your system. You will hear a big difference on high end phones but even low end devices will profit from this drivers. DSP Manager will likely not work on many devices.
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.motioncoding.beats&feature=nav_result#?t=W251bGwsMSwxLDMsImNvbS5tb3Rpb25jb2RpbmcuYmVhdHMiXQ..

Made my HTC Evo 3D completely silent. Uninstalling did not resolve this. Now I can't here anything in calls, the ringtones are not sounding and the alarms are silent. No sound what so ever. I'm just sayin'...
